{"tid":2046631,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"香港 MineCraft 原味生存娛樂伺服器1.15.2","createTime":"2020-06-01T13:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T04:37:48.000Z","uid":153199,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"da438cafd645ea1cba897aec7aa0cb82c654bb49","tid":2046631,"uid":153199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T13:58:49.000Z","msg":"【血色幽默】原味生存娛樂 | MCMMO | Slimefun繁化 | 寵物系統 | 精英怪物<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ecp8gde.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEcp8gde.png&h=425cd919&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">伺服器名稱：血色幽默BloodHumor<br />\n遊戲版本：1.15.2<br />\n正版驗證：開啟<br />\n白名單：開啟<br />\n連線位址：mc.bhhk.online<br />\n最高遊玩人數：30<br />\n開放時間：24小時開啟<br />\n狀態圖：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://minecraft-mp.com/banner-258930.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fminecraft-mp.com%2Fbanner-258930.png&h=c57dfb48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">其他介紹：<br />\n目前伺服器為公測階段，開服至今僅有兩個月，雖然大多數功能已完善，但仍有很多不足之處，管理員已持續兩個月不斷更新伺服器至今，本次為第二次公開給玩家遊玩，首次為封測階段。<br />\n申請白名單方法: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cqACgh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cqACgh&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=3700e6d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cqACgh</a> (MineCraft成員可以忽視必須有麥克風此規則)<br />\n遊戲難度: 困難(精英怪物)<br />\n遊戲模式: 生存模式</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TFc2kGy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTFc2kGy.png&h=04cde1e1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">*加入伺服器後，按Shift+F便可以打開選單</span><br />\n此選單為主選單，按下不同的按鈕可以進入不同的內選單。<br />\n插件繁多，不能盡錄，期待你加入測試伺服器-w-&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3057wOs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3057wOs.png&h=4257eb49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">聊天室中[&hearts;]顯示為婚姻狀態，滑鼠移向即可查詢伴侶名字，點擊即可查詢指令。<br />\n聊天室中[交易]，點擊即可與該玩家進行交易。<br />\n聊天室中[傳送]，點擊即可對該玩家發出傳送到他身邊的請求。<br />\n聊天室中[$]，點擊再輸入金額，確定(ENTER)後即可給予該玩家金幣。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JpkSHVm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJpkSHVm.png&h=7e0e54c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n封測玩家建築眾多，有興趣進服去看看吧，XDD!<br />\n獻上部份封測玩家大合照吧@@<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34i1Bfr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34i1Bfr.jpg&h=42952915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">管理員至今仍對遊戲抱有大量熱情，期待你的加入可以令伺服器更美好！<br />\n你的加入是管理員繼續更新伺服器的動力，管理員知道雖然我不是個最好的，但我是個願意改善到最好的，我深知永遠不能做最好，但我願意去盡力做到最好。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;期待，你的到來。<br />\n<br />\n祝 看到這裡的各位 看到的那天 整天也快樂</span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JwFGBfE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJwFGBfE.png&h=884c1636&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"393822e4d8c8e68d801390c995a6aa2627909f3f","tid":2046631,"uid":140710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:00:31.000Z","msg":"Ser主係奸商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78ffb56cab288578a8aa6e20eb5c2ba8f51d1c6","tid":2046631,"uid":140710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"393822e4d8c8e68d801390c995a6aa2627909f3f","tid":2046631,"uid":140710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:00:31.000Z","msg":"Ser主係奸商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T14:02:22.000Z","msg":"仲要係渣男<br />\n呃左好多人隻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8454f22893dab5cf7aa6a3b5892a1bc08efdb43d","tid":2046631,"uid":198402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:30:04.000Z","msg":"白名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif